a 17th century, 1629 book.

00:46:32.060 --> 00:46:36.420
And I say that what
are classics for?

00:46:36.420 --> 00:46:38.470
What is the use of classics?

00:46:38.470 --> 00:46:42.720
Is not to have a good degree in
