a classic to give an order

00:46:58.880 --> 00:47:04.430
and understand something having
a reading of when we leave.

00:47:04.430 --> 00:47:09.920
In that way I use everything
that I was having access to

00:47:09.920 --> 00:47:12.990
and I spend a lot of
time and I read a lot.

00:47:12.990 --> 00:47:17.950 position:56%
But, you know, influences never jump
directly from one book to the other.

00:47:17.950 --> 00:47:20.810
You eat them and you sweat them.

00:47:20.810 --> 00:47:23.870
